<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  Civilopedia entries for the mod's concepts. Adds a dedicated "Emigration" section
  (pattern from the corpus mod 3640054014 "ORN") with an overview page + one page per
  system, reusing the base "Concept" page layout (its single CONTENT chapter). Body
  text is one rich paragraph per page (LOC keys, with [n] line breaks), localized in
  text/<locale>/ModText.xml like everything else. Loaded via the modinfo
  <UpdateDatabase> data ActionGroup.

  The Open/Closed Borders policy cards get their own pedia pages automatically from
  their Tradition Name/Description (data/emigration-policies.xml), so they aren't
  repeated here.
-->
